Sunbelt Securities - Institutional





 




  HomeAdvisorsClientsInstitutionalContact Us
 


INSTITUTIONAL TRADING
Sunbelts institutional division provides the sales and trading of all Fixed Income Instruments, Equities and Portfolio trading. These services meet the needs of our institutional clients, which include; corporations, insurance companies, mutual fund companies, broker/dealers, banks, municipalities, pension funds, and other financial institutions. 
The combination of our experience, expertise, systems and services help ensure that our institutional clients meet their business objectives and finance their capital needs. We are large enough to serve their needs yet small enough to provide unique, custom solutions. 
EQUITY TRADING
All of Sunbelts Institutional Equity Traders have over 25 years of trading experience. Our team oriented approach, coupled with our long standing trading relationships allows us to provide our clients with personalized service by experienced professionals. This continues to be of utmost importance as the markets remain volatile. Our equity and trading department takes pride in providing best execution from trade initiation to settlement. Our trading desk trades billions of dollars in securities each year. 
FIXED INCOME TRADING

UNIQUE PERSPECTIVE
At Sunbelt Securities, the decades of experience behind our institutional fixed income team include not only sales and trading, but also portfolio management. This gives us a unique position among todays broker/dealers, bringing a buy-side perspective to better understand our clients investment process and meet their needs. Our proprietary research and strategy- from quantitative models to portfolio structuring tools- is tailored to each individual client.




      BEST EXECUTION
Our experienced traders work to deliver unparalleled execution for our clients. Constant communication between traders and salespeople ensures first-hand knowledge of market conditions as they evolve. 




      BROAD VISION
At Sunbelt, we arent interested in narrowing our clients range of choices to our inventory alone. Our unique software solutions allow our traders and salespeople to instantly locate any available security in the fixed income universe. This allows for better price discovery across comparable securities, an unmatched menu of securities available for purchase and enhanced liquidity for sell orders.




      CORE EXPERTISE
Sunbelt is active in all sectors of the fixed income market, including MBS, ABS, CMBS, corporate debt and municipals. We specialize in the trading and analysis of complex structured securities in the CMO, ABS, CMBS and securitized residential mortgage arenas. 
  
 

